data.description: *OPEN HOUSE SAT 3-2-24 2-4PM* Nestled in a half-acre within an original Flower Mound lakeside neighborhood, this beautiful two-story lake cottage is 2,634 square feet! When you first approach the inviting entry, a courtyard welcomes you. As you enter inside, you are surrounded by windows in the living room and kitchen area unleashing an abundance of natural light. This custom build offers four bedrooms, including a spacious owner's retreat, two full baths, a sun room, a converted storage room now a sophisticated home office, and a remodeled kitchen with marble countertops and a marble kitchen island, merging modern design with practicality. The upper-level retreat features a balcony, abundant windows, a dry bar, double sinks, and a spacious closet. The backyard provides an oasis of nature and wildlife scenery.  The Corp of Engineers is behind the home along with direct access to Northshore bike trails and Twin Coves Marina. Located near DFW Airport and more.
